description:
This is a 10 minute workout called 'BEGINNER Full Body Calisthenics Workout (Preparation Phase | 30 minutes)' from the channel The Bodyweight Process.
The workout falls under Strength/Calisthenics and Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Other for this workout.
The workout has a The Foundation Builder and The Masterclass Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Hey guys welcome back, in this video I'll be providing you guys a Beginner full body calisthenics (circuit based) workout routine. This routine is perfect for those who are just starting their calisthenics training or who want to get a time efficient workout in. If you don't have access to a park, I provide alternatives that you can apply.

 This routine covers all the fundamental compound movements that you'll want to master in calisthenics and will prepare you well for future strength training. This routines overall purpose is to prepare you for strength training, but can also be used for a solid workout while working on the basics in a time efficient manner. Hope you guys enjoy it!
